me.Abhigya.core.util.lang

Interface PluginInternalLanguageEnumContainer


  • public interface PluginInternalLanguageEnumContainer
    Like the name says, this is a container for the different internal languages that a Plugin may support. The Plugin loads the configuration of a specific language and saves it on a PluginInternalLanguageEnumContainer, then the plugin can use that language for internal process. Note that the PluginInternalLanguageEnumContainers must have only the internal language of the plugin, the containers are not intended to be configured externally in any way!
